Prioritize ATP objectives as curriculum constraints.

[QUESTION_DESIGN_RULES]
- Frame questions around real Indonesian scenarios.
- Avoid simple recall questions ("Sebutkan", "Apa definisi").
- Require students to explain "Mengapa" or "Bagaimana".
- Do not make the question overly convoluted.

[RUBRIC_REQUIREMENTS]
- Keep rubrics concise and actionable.
- Define exactly what constitutes a high-score answer.

[EXPLANATION_REQUIREMENTS]
- Keep explanation direct and focused on the key concepts.
- Use clear cause-effect logic.

[STRICT_OUTPUT_RULES]
- Return raw JSON only.
- No markdown code block.
- No additional commentary.
- Escape newline characters.
- Escape internal quotes.
